data.description: Come check out this desirable 4 bed, 3.5 Bath Townhome in the Exclusive and Gated Odyssey Club of Tinley Park!!! Step inside to the 2 story entry way opening right up to a spacious living room with stunning hardwood flooring, Gas fireplace, gorgeous window wall and Cathedral ceiling. Next is the highly coveted Main Floor Primary Bedroom suite with full bath and large walk in closet! The main floor also features a powder room for guest, laundry room and a nice sized Kitchen with granite countertops, cozy breakfast area, and stainless-steel appliances. The 2nd floor boast a Gorgeous Catwalk View that leads to 2 more bedrooms and a Jack and Jill full bath with separate shower. The fully finished basement with huge family room is great for entertaining and has lots of storage space as well as an additional nice sized bedroom and another Full bath with a double walk in shower. The 2 car attached garage and a spacious deck area for Grillin and Chillin just continue to add to the appeal of this Townhome! Come take a look today at your new home!
